author: Joshua Nelson
title: Tom Cotton: China's cover-up of COVID-19 was deadliest and costliest in human history
description: Sen. Tom Cotton said on Friday that China’s cover-up of the origin of the coronavirus outbreak may have been the “deadliest and costliest” move in human history.
